        <lcInstruction>
            <p>The &lt;example> element allows you to show an example of the entire task. The
                &lt;stepxmp> element is similar, but it show an example relevant to a single step
                instead of an example relevant to the entire task.  </p>
            <p><xref href="https://youtu.be/kQS7FCSLJ7E" format="html" scope="external">Video:
                    Adding an example in a DITA task</xref></p>
        </lcInstruction>
